# Canonical path after mutation

## Rule

After mutating a file path or artifact location, update every reference to the
old path before returning or persisting success.

## Check references

1. Local variables.
2. Database columns.
3. Job payloads.
4. Return values and API responses.
5. Download links and manifests.
6. Upload/backup calls.
7. Logs and audit records.
8. Cleanup routines.
9. Tests and fixtures.
10. Docs and runbooks.

## Pre-commit check

- [ ] Old path no longer appears in active code paths.
- [ ] DB/job/API references point to the canonical path.
- [ ] Cleanup does not delete the new artifact accidentally.
